Matt’s Minutes: Qualified Charitable Contributions (June 2017)
Posted on June 28, 2017 
Dan fills in for Matt this month to discuss how you can use Qualified Charitable Distributions to satisfy your Required Minimum Distribution once you reach the age of 70.5. Not yet 70.5 years young but know someone who is? Make sure to do them a favor and share this information with them! Access the Closed Captions here.
For more information on the requirements of Qualified Charitable Distributions, please visit: http://promo.richmondbrothers.com/QCD
 

 
